BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:resmtl-15
SEQUENCE:0
DTSTAMP:20260310T034710
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260312T173000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260312T193000
SUMMARY:RadMedic first aid training
LOCATION:(métro Préfontaine)
DESCRIPTION:2026-03-12 17:30:00\n\n(métro Préfontaine)\n\nhttps://www.op
 enstreetmap.org/node/11973307079\n\nRadMedics is an activist medic group t
 hat hosts workshops on how to provide first aid in protest and street sett
 ings. The group is organizing a hands on experience for protest first aid\
 , specifically focusing on moving people and dealing with chemical contami
 nants in the eyes. Bring a buddy\, your first aid kits\, and some clothing
  to be dragged around in! We'll have light snacks to have at the break et 
 la traduction envers le français est possible\, si nécessaire.&nbsp\;
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.openstreetmap.org/node/11973307079
END:VEVENT
