SUMMARY:Film: "Partners"
LOCATION:(to be announced)
DESCRIPTION:2026-03-12 19:00:00\n\n(to be announced)\n\nYour union AGSEM\,
  in partnership with Working Films\, invites all members (and friends!) to
  a free screening of&nbsp\;Partners.&nbsp\;\n&nbsp\;\nThe film shares the 
 story of how a group of baristas in Buffalo\, New York announce their inte
 ntion to form a labor union\, and how Starbucks responds with an elaborate
  and illegal anti-union campaign.&nbsp\;\n&nbsp\;\nFeaturing on-the-ground
  footage from workers and organizers\, Partners takes us to the front line
 s of the historic union campaign that catalyzed America’s Gen Z labor re
 vival. The screening will take place on March 12\, 2026 at 7PM- location T
 BA!&nbsp\;
END:VEVENT
