  Guy)\n\nhttps://www.openstreetmap.org/node/4035248248\n\nThis stirring hi
 storical film depicts a 1974 Indigenous youth occupation in Kenora\, focus
 ing on Louie Cameron: the leader of the Ojibway Warrior Society.
